methods.convert:
Converts between the value in the column and the return value of the provider.

:param v: (java.lang.Object) - raw value from the column
:return: (IndexableDataTable.T) raw value converted into the desired data value
methods.get:
Gets the value at the given index.

:param index: (int) - index
:return: (IndexableDataTable.T) value of this dataset at index
methods.size:
Gets the size of this dataset.

:return: (int) the size of this dataset

text: IndexableData dataset whose data is a column in a table and whose indices are the row numbers of the column.
